{"tid":1863243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如去政總賣口罩","createTime":"2020-02-05T05:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T06:06:59.000Z","uid":301586,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3490eee163190f21a780d285c677f8515b664d85","tid":1863243,"uid":301586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"宜家陸續有舖頭有口罩番<br />\n一發出去話可以排隊攞籌買口罩就排隊排到集會咁<br />\n如果攞籌係去政總排隊 有籌先去舖頭俾錢攞口罩 大家順便一路排隊一路嗌林鄭封關 唔嗌就冇籌拎<br />\n反正啲人都草左喺到 黎得買口罩都唔想死 唔好晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/05/130611_5a9908a14faf2c5a7edeb368aa45710e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F05%2F130611_5a9908a14faf2c5a7edeb368aa45710e.jpg&h=7fe62fec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70a8a5037d347fe9efca0af89a84b9794f057bb0","tid":1863243,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7b93ce05f696340f9fce17764a5e81e28065bb3","tid":1863243,"uid":100999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a0a88597f5855bf6d24e9ea96953525c17a395","tid":1863243,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc65b32d50a0c3fcea90e86df03a68dd6516011e","tid":1863243,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"一定比狗沒收<img src=\"/assets/f